mawojN, 
[a coll. gen. n., Waves; billows; surges; or a collection of waves;] water rising above other water: (TA:) pl. OamowaAjN: (Ṣ, Ḳ, Mṣb:) mawojapN has a more special signification; 
[namely, a wave, a single wave;] and the pl. of this, which is the n. un., is mawojaAtN. (Mṣb.)
